<p>arcessere is quite generally to summon or call for someone of any rank, to ask someone to come.</p>
<p>accire is to call for or invite someone who is regarded as an equal, often to entreat someone to come.</p>
<p>evocare is to summon an inferior, and to command him to come.</p>
